<a href="https://github.com/tonyspiro/gulp-mamp" target="_blank">https://github.com/tonyspiro/gulp-mamp</a>

And npm:
<a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/gulp-mamp/" target="_blank">https://www.npmjs.com/package/gulp-mamp/</a>

